prompt.expectations: I wanted to find a quick result for my question for writing Test plan, instead of using Google search.
prompt.examplePrompt: I want you to act as a software testing engineer. Give me please entry criteria for test process which I can write in test plan.
prompt.sideEffectsOrComments: I saved my time because I got results in a several second instead of opening a lot of pages during using Google search. Of course it is necessary to analyze  this information and adapted to my project but it will not take a lot of time.

assessment.comments: Good prompt, but the user kinda limited the model. It could have generated a good document to start with.
